*Hteli* smo da učestvujemo u maratonu, ali nismo uspeli da se prijavimo na vreme. (We wanted to participate in the marathon, but we didn't manage to register in time.)

*Hteo* je da pokaže da je najbolji u klasi. (He wanted to show that he was the best in the class.)

*Htela* je da joj devojka pomogne da dođe na vreme. (She wanted her friend to help her arrive on time.)

*Hteli* bismo da znamo gde je ona. (We would like to know where she is.)

*Htevši* da stigne na vreme, trčao je cijelim putem. (Trying to arrive on time, he ran the whole way.)